00401 static void rna_StateActuator_state_set(PointerRNA *ptr, const int *values)
00402 {
00403     bActuator *act = (bActuator*)ptr->data;
00404     bStateActuator *sa = act->data;
00405 
00406     int i, tot = 0;
00407 
00408     /* ensure we always have some state selected */
00409     for (i = 0; i<OB_MAX_STATES; i++)
00410         if (values[i])
00411             tot++;

00413     if (tot == 0)
00414         return;
00415 
00416     for (i = 0; i<OB_MAX_STATES; i++) {
00417         if (values[i]) sa->mask |= (1<<i);
00418         else sa->mask &= ~(1<<i);

00467 static void rna_Actuator_Armature_update(Main *UNUSED(bmain), Scene *UNUSED(scene), PointerRNA *ptr)
00468 {
00469     bActuator *act = (bActuator *)ptr->data;
00470     bArmatureActuator *aa = act->data;
00471     Object *ob = (Object *)ptr->id.data;
00472 
00473     char *posechannel = aa->posechannel;
00474     char *constraint = aa->constraint;
00475 
00476     /* check that bone exist in the active object */
00477     if (ob->type == OB_ARMATURE && ob->pose) {
00478         bPoseChannel *pchan;
00479         bPose *pose = ob->pose;
00480         for (pchan = pose->chanbase.first; pchan; pchan = pchan->next) {
00481             if (!strcmp(pchan->name, posechannel)) {
00482                 /* found it, now look for constraint channel */
00483                 bConstraint *con;
00484                 for (con = pchan->constraints.first; con; con = con->next) {
00485                     if (!strcmp(con->name, constraint)) {
00486                         /* found it, all ok */
00487                         return;
00488                     }
00489                 }
00490                 /* didn't find constraint, make empty */
00491                 constraint[0] = 0;
00492                 return;
00493             }
00494         }
00495     }
00496     /* didn't find any */
00497     posechannel[0] = 0;
00498     constraint[0] = 0;
00499 }
